You know what real terror is?

00:23:37.751 --> 00:23:38.918 position:50% align:center
I do.

00:23:39.002 --> 00:23:41.338 position:50% align:center
Try something jumping
at you without warning!

00:23:41.421 --> 00:23:42.505 position:50% align:center
'Cause when it happens,

00:23:42.589 --> 00:23:43.923 position:50% align:center
you know there's
another scare on the way.

00:23:44.007 --> 00:23:45.508 position:50% align:center
You just don't know when!

00:23:45.592 --> 00:23:48.178 position:50% align:center
Next time, episode 11,
"She Looks"!

